Wavelength

Each player will see a number on a spectrum (e.g., Casual ‚Üî Formal). They give one short clue that hints at how far toward one end the target sits. Their partner places a pointer on the spectrum where they think the target is. You will get points assigned to how close you are to the target. Please ping me when you have a duo ready to take part in this.
